<div id="main">

<h2>Strawberry Milkshake</h2>
<img src="../strawberry-milkshake/strawberrymilkshake.jpg" alt="Strawberry Milkshake" style="width:300px;height:300px;">

<h3>Ingrediets Required:</h3>
<ul>
   <li>Strawberries (100g)</li>
   <li>Milk (300ml)</li>
   <li>Vanilla Ice-cream (2 Scoops)</li>
   <li>Icing Sugar(2 tbsp.)</li>
  
</ul>

<h3>Method:</h3>
<ol>
   <li>Begin by removing the stems from the strawberries.</li>
   <li>Add the strawberries, ince-cream, icing sugar and milk into the blender, and begin to blend, start from slow speeds then work your way up.</li>
   <li>When mixture is unifrom pour contents into a glass and serve.</li>
</ol>
<p>Enjoy your drink!</p>
</ol>
